{"tid":1788685,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FC科隆決定不再在支那舉辦足球學院","createTime":"2019-12-19T01:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T01:29:58.000Z","uid":273294,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90f339965da09b56b68f1fb94dfd6c2de95870db","tid":1788685,"uid":273294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/dec/18/fc-cologne-pull-out-of-running-football-academy-in-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2F2019%2Fdec%2F18%2Ffc-cologne-pull-out-of-running-football-academy-in-china&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6rYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=ea0d032c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/dec/18/fc-cologne-pull-out-of-running-football-academy-in-china</a><br />\n<br />\n摘要：由於阿森納同義士奥斯爾割席，球會決定不再在支那舉辦足球學院，損失約1.8百萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n董事會成員認為「支那人權問題長期被忽略，國家繼續監視人民，比奧威爾（Orwell) 所想更甚。」「所以FC科隆不應在支那活動。搵錢唔係一切。作為一間活躍於社會嘅非盈利機構，我哋唔可以支持一個殘暴不仁，極權專制嘅政府。<br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，德國戰線極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b7c72e19567a695de105f427ca4b3b8e38835feb","tid":1788685,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6rYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=519d1fad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https